*! _fjcoint_cv_lambda.ado
*! 5% critical values for Fourier Lambda-max test
*! Source: Pascalau, Lee, Nazlioglu & Lu (2022), Online Appendix
*! Part of fjcoint package

program define _fjcoint_cv_lambda, rclass
  version 14.0
  
